headline: Prediction: Buying Medtronic Today Will Set You Up for Life
summary: Healthcare can be a complex sector, and it is one that I long ago decided to outsource to the industry professionals who run closed-end fund Blackrock Health Sciences Trust.  One of the big reasons why I avoid most healthcare stocks is that the pace of innovation is swift, and I just don't have the expertise (or the time) to keep up with the sector's ongoing evolution.
